EnabledOrNot.name: EnabledOrNot
EnabledOrNot.description: An indication of whether a feature is configured as enabled or disabled.

ActiveOrNot.name: ActiveOrNot
ActiveOrNot.description: An indication of whether an IP address is active or inactive.

IpAddressType.name: IpAddressType
IpAddressType.description: The type of an IP address (IPv4, IPv6 user configured, IPv6 link local, or IPv6 autoconfig).

hostIpTable.name: hostIpTable
hostIpTable.description: Table of IP addresses on the device and their attributes.

hostIpEntry.name: hostIpEntry
hostIpEntry.description: An entry in the host IP address table. Rows cannot be created or deleted.

hostIpIndex.name: hostIpIndex
hostIpIndex.description: Index into the IP address table, starting with 1.

hostIpAddress.name: hostIpAddress
hostIpAddress.description: String representation of an IP address, in CIDR format.

hostIpType.name: hostIpType
hostIpType.description: Whether this IP address is IPv4 or IPv6 and how it was configured.

hostIpActive.name: hostIpActive
hostIpActive.description: Whether this IP address is active.

hostIPv6Enabled.name: hostIPv6Enabled
hostIPv6Enabled.description: Whether IPv6 is enabled on the device.

hostIPv6AutoConfig.name: hostIPv6AutoConfig
hostIPv6AutoConfig.description: Whether IPv6 autoconfig is enabled on the device.
